WEBVTT

1
00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:20.140 
Oh! Morning, Spiros. Sleep well?

2
00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:20.140 
早上好 斯皮罗 睡的好吗

3
00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:22.370 
Yes, despite a goat with a cough

4
00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:22.370 
还好 不过有只咳嗽的山羊

5
00:01:22.370 --> 00:01:24.150 
finding its way up into the attic.

6
00:01:22.370 --> 00:01:24.150 
一直在找上阁楼的路

7
00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:29.040 
Then the weasels sat on my face.

8
00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:29.040 
还有黄鼠狼坐到了我的脸上

9
00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.190 
Lemurs.

10
00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.190 
是狐猴

11
00:01:30.190 --> 00:01:32.490 
Sorry, darling, but Spiros is working hard

12
00:01:30.190 --> 00:01:32.490 
不好意思 亲爱的 但斯皮罗很卖力地帮你

13
00:01:32.490 --> 00:01:33.940 
building your animal enclosures.

14
00:01:32.490 --> 00:01:33.940 
建你的动物园

15
00:01:33.940 --> 00:01:36.670 
Course, ideally, they'd all just roam.

16
00:01:33.940 --> 00:01:36.670 
当然 放养是最理想的

17
00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.200 
Yeah, then ideally

18
00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.200 
用我的李-恩菲尔德步枪

19
00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.890 
we'd hunt them down with my Lee-Enfield

20
00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.890 
猎捕它们也是很理想的

21
00:01:41.890 --> 00:01:43.200 
and put them in a pie.

22
00:01:41.890 --> 00:01:43.200 
把它们做成馅饼

23
00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:47.970 
Where shall I leave my laundry?

24
00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:47.970 
我应该把脏衣服放哪

25
00:01:47.970 --> 00:01:50.320 
Oh, I'll take it, thank you.

26
00:01:47.970 --> 00:01:50.320 
给我吧 谢谢

